Package com.pantgwyn.objectsort

Class FileWrapper<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pantgwyn.objectsort.FileWrapper<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The class of objects being sorted
    public class FileWrapper<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A encapsulation of the work files used by ObjectSort.

    An instance of FileWrapper is created for every sort work file required (if any) to perform the sort. The work files are only used if the sort cannot be completed in memory.

    Author:
    Dave Breeze
